title: One Direction was never Zayn Malik's 'kind of bag': Liam Payne
text:
*London:* One Direction member Liam Payne shared that he understands why former band member Zayn Malik left the band as the band's music was not exactly Malik's "kind of bag".
*Liam Payne. Pic/Santa Banta*
Payne added that Malik's "taste in music was a bit different", reports femalefirst.co.uk.
